*'''Golden Armor''': The Watcher possesses a golden armor that he used for combat. He wore the armor during a fight with [[Infinity Ultron/Age of Ultron|Ultron]].

==Facilities==
*'''[[Observational Plane]]''': The Watcher resides in the Observational Plane, where he observes all realities within the [[Multiverse]].

